1
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:10,224
HAIDER: We've been planning this for weeks, Iqrash. Hadi's got a reputation for being untouchable on the track.

2
00:00:10,224 --> 00:00:14,688
IQRASH: We're not just going to take him down on the track, Haider. We're going to make it personal.

3
00:00:14,688 --> 00:00:16,560
HADI OFFSCREEN: I'm not afraid of you two.

4
00:00:16,560 --> 00:00:19,056
HAIDER: Oh, I think you should be.

5
00:00:19,056 --> 00:00:26,592
HAMMAD: Wait, let's not do this. There's an annual car race coming up. Why don't we settle it there?

6
00:00:26,592 --> 00:00:31,584
HAIDER: And put ourselves at the mercy of the judges? No way.

7
00:00:31,584 --> 00:00:35,314
HADI: I've got the edge I need. Time to take these guys down.

8
00:00:35,314 --> 00:00:39,562
HAMMAD: Good luck, Hadi. I'll be rooting for you.

9
00:00:39,562 --> 00:00:48,908
ANNOUNCER VO: Welcome to the annual city car race! Your drivers include Hadi in the sleek blue car, Haider in the rugged red car, and many more!

10
00:00:48,908 --> 00:00:50,238
HADI: I'm taking the lead!

11
00:00:50,238 --> 00:00:54,246
HAIDER: No way! I'm not letting you win!

12
00:00:54,246 --> 00:00:55,144
HADI: I did it!
